title: Colmar, Illinois
content:
Colmar is an unincorporated community in Lamoine Township, McDonough County, Illinois, United States. Colmar is located on Illinois Route 61, 4 miles (6.4Â km) north-northeast of Plymouth.[2] Colmar had a post office, which closed on July 18, 1992.[3]
